{
  "stem": "323.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No one told me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother told me what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that they had broken-- that the store was completely-- all the windows were smashed in in my uncle's store, that the temple was demolished, that the Germans didn't like Jews anymore.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I mean I kept saying, well, why?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, what have we done or something?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it's very hard to understand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, well, she doesn't know anything we have done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they just don't like this anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mean, how can I-- at the time, I was nine years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So how can you explain that to-- or seven-- to a nine-year-old or a seven-year-old, really?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened after that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened to the store?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The store was then taken over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, they had signs on it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't buy from Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They made it so that it was no longer profitable to keep the store.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my uncle was forced to sell it at a price that the Germans stipulated that he sell it for.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And consequently, they left in '39 and came to the United States, my uncle, his wife, and their two children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you stayed-- your family stayed in-- I don't think-- see, I, I was too young to realize it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I don't know why we didn't get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think part of it was money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because my aunt who died five years ago had given me a bunch of letters that my parents wrote to them, one is dated '42 yet.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it's pathetic, because all my father is asking, get us out, get us out, get us out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I mean, I'm going to be very honest with you.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
